OL,6,FA metal detectorist jailed for trying
OL,7,Fto sell Anglo-Saxon coins to an
OL,8,Fundercover police officer he thought
OL,9,Fwas an expert working for a wealthy
OL,10,FAmerican buyer has been ordered to
OL,11,Frepay #103,000.
OL,13,FRoger Pilling, 77, from Loveclough,
OL,14,FLancashire, has three months to repay
OL,15,Fthe money or he could face another 12-
OL,16,Fmonth prison sentence.
