OL,6,FPilling and his co-defendant Craig
OL,7,FBest, 48, previously of Bishop
OL,8,FAuckland, County Durham, tried to sell
OL,9,Fthe coins to a real American
OL,10,Fcollector, who contacted UK experts
OL,11,Fabout how such rare pieces were
OL,12,Favailable for sale, and police were
OL,13,Fcalled in.
OL,15,FForty-four coins were recovered in the
OL,16,Ffollowing sting operation but two `
OL,17,Fthat Pilling claimed he had broken `
OL,18,Fwere never found.
