OL,6,FOn 24 April 2025, Pilling was ordered
OL,7,Fto repay #103,000 after a confiscation
OL,8,Forder was granted at Teeside Crown
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FHe has three months to make the
OL,12,Fpayment or he could face another 12-
OL,13,Fmonth prison sentence.
OL,15,FAdrian Foster, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,16,Ffor the CPS Proceeds of Crime
OL,17,FDivision, said: "Roger Pilling
OL,18,Fintended to sell these rare and
OL,19,Fimportant coins for his own gain.
