OL,6,F"We will always work to ensure that
OL,7,Fcrime does not pay, and criminals
OL,8,Fcannot benefit from their ill-gotten
OL,9,Fgains."
OL,11,FThe coins were estimated to have been
OL,12,Fmade between 874 CE and 879 CE.
OL,14,FThe sentencing judge found that the 44
OL,15,Fcoins were part of a larger,
OL,16,Fundeclared find known as the
OL,17,FHerefordshire or Leominster Hoard,
OL,18,Fwhich was discovered in 2015 and is
OL,19,Fworth millions of pounds, but which
OL,20,Fwas also not declared.
